I have my own room too... but I might prefer... spending
time here with everyone...

...As for Vega, you know... she drinks a lot of water while
studying, so she goes to the bathroom... quite frequently...

\SM[rock]\SE[22]Good morning. What's up? \SE[0]You seem
really happy.

\SE[12]Good morning...! \.I'm glad you asked!
\!\SM[pop]\SE[13]That thing I was secretly developing, you
know, it's finally complete...!!

\SE[13]The shitty game that I made is finally complete!!
\!\SM[double]\SE[12]I named it Laura DASH!!

\SE[19]Laura DASH!!...!? \SE[1]Or should I say, Shitty
game...? What is it?

\SE[10]Laura, don't you know about shitty games!?
\SE[15]It's actually an incredibly shitty game...! \SE[17]In
this day and age, there are even people making a fortune
from shitty games!

\SE[5]I-Is that so...? \SE[3]Isn't it better to make an
interesting game...?

\SM[nod]\SE[15]No, words are unnecessary. Please experience
my shitty game. \!\SE[1]...Oh, is it okay if you waste some
time?
\SE[1]Um... Do I just need to turn on this switch?
スライドスピード = def
\SE[2]Huh...? Nothing in particular is happening though...

\SE[109]Huh, what...! \!\SM[rock]\SE[53]Something was put on
my head...!

\SM[tremble]\SE[31]S-Something has been put on my hands and
feet...!? I can't move... at all...!!
スライドスピード = def

I have my own room too... but I might prefer... spending
time here with everyone...

...As for Vega, you know... she drinks a lot of water while
studying, so she goes to the bathroom... quite frequently...

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The
flames here are the most comforting.
